layout.text:
Wishbone Reserve is the love child of two devoted vintage & design obsessed friends, Athena Hoffberger & Julie Lilienfeld.
They are passionate about the one-off, the gently loved, and the amazingly well-made treasure. Their mission is to delight their customers and fans, lovingly referred to as "Wishboners."
By hosting an ever changing array of interesting antiques and collectibles, their team ensures the joy, comfort, and style that only great vintage home goods can provide.
